dc_title_s: Exquisita & magno aliquot mensium periculo lustrata et iam retecta Freti Magellanici Facies = Eijgentlicke afbeeldinghe der Magellanischer Strate : die nu met veel gevaers ettelijeke Maenden doorsien, van nieus ondeckt is
dc_description_s: Publication information in Spanish. Relief shown pictorially. Depths shown by soundings. Oriented with north to bottom. "Descripción del mapa: Estrecho de Magallanes. Original impreso en 1630." Includes inset of "Dese eijlanden die in gheene Pascaerten aengeteeckent bevonden en worden, ...."
dc_subject_sm: Magellan, Strait of (Chile and Argentina)—Maps—Early works to 1800—Facsimiles
